{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Have you ever wanted to fight a Minotaur? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Right now, you can battle the Minotaur and other powerful, dangerous mythological monsters like the Basilisk, the Kraken, and Medusa. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>The exciting fight of your life, against ten of the famous mythological monsters, from legends and folklore. </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(+15,000 has downloaded my Demo, so far.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Fighter: Wield a sword, improve it, and even enhance it with magic. Face off against ten mythological monsters in the first main mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Rogue: Master the art of stealth, equip throwing stars or daggers, and sneak into dragon hideouts to deliver a deadly backstab that could even decapitate them\u2014or perhaps just steal some of their precious treasures. This is the second main mission: finding the lost Dragon Orbs that control the dragons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Wizard: Choose your magic school\u2014focus on war, defense, or even the dark art of necromancy. Harness the power within you to fight undead beasts, and in time, you may even gain control over them. This is the final main mission, but its secrets will remain hidden... for now. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This is the Minotaur, and you can find it on the first of eleven maps.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078610/extras/MinotaurAxe-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738741505\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Magic in this game is wild...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It has to be because you are fighting against mythical creatures like Minotaurs, Medusa, and the Basilisk, which can paralyze. And deep beneath the dwarf kingdom in the North, there are rumors of something dark waiting to be released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is an open-world, single player RPG game.<br>You can play it casually, taking your time to do quests and explore the world, or you can play it more hard-core. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I like to play open-world RPGs like Skyrim, Oblivion, and Morrowind, as well as Two Worlds II. So, I have taken the parts I like from them: the wild magic and alchemy from Morrowind, the bright colors from Oblivion, and Skyrim's weapon improvements.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738741505","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078610/page.bg.jpg?t=1738741505","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078610/168b8e35ca8528c28e66a703aa1198b2fd183ebc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738741505","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078610/168b8e35ca8528c28e66a703aa1198b2fd183ebc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738741505","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2614440,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Have you ever wanted to fight a Minotaur? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Right now, you can battle the Minotaur and other powerful, dangerous mythological monsters like the Basilisk, the Kraken, and Medusa. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>The exciting fight of your life, against ten of the famous mythological monsters, from legends and folklore. </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(+15,000 has downloaded my Demo, so far.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Fighter: Wield a sword, improve it, and even enhance it with magic. Face off against ten mythological monsters in the first main mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Rogue: Master the art of stealth, equip throwing stars or daggers, and sneak into dragon hideouts to deliver a deadly backstab that could even decapitate them\u2014or perhaps just steal some of their precious treasures. This is the second main mission: finding the lost Dragon Orbs that control the dragons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Wizard: Choose your magic school\u2014focus on war, defense, or even the dark art of necromancy. Harness the power within you to fight undead beasts, and in time, you may even gain control over them. This is the final main mission, but its secrets will remain hidden... for now. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This is the Minotaur, and you can find it on the first of eleven maps.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078610/extras/MinotaurAxe-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738741505\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Magic in this game is wild...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It has to be because you are fighting against mythical creatures like Minotaurs, Medusa, and the Basilisk, which can paralyze. And deep beneath the dwarf kingdom in the North, there are rumors of something dark waiting to be released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is an open-world, single player RPG game.<br>You can play it casually, taking your time to do quests and explore the world, or you can play it more hard-core. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I like to play open-world RPGs like Skyrim, Oblivion, and Morrowind, as well as Two Worlds II. So, I have taken the parts I like from them: the wild magic and alchemy from Morrowind, the bright colors from Oblivion, and Skyrim's weapon improvements.</p>","developers":["J. C. SpringBourne"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078610/header.jpg?t=1738741505","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257086505,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257086505/movie480.mp4?t=1738741502","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257086505/movie_max.mp4?t=1738741502"},"name":"1st Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257086505/08ad39ede4402fd8aae0a5cf8b206b4e55f13b62/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1738741502","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257086505/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1738741502","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257086505/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1738741502"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257094414,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257094414/movie480.mp4?t=1738600443","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257094414/movie_max.mp4?t=1738600443"},"name":"Dragon Attack","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257094414/63a56af3b799fbc4e4c31b9fdaac832035c58064/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1738600443","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257094414/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1738600443","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257094414/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1738600443"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257047093,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257047093/movie480.mp4?t=1723890757","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257047093/movie_max.mp4?t=1723890757"},"name":"StartScene","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257047093/movie.29